    ('message("\\"That old cradle was the cradle used to rock Gorn the Barbarian to sleep at night when he was just a baby. Thou canst see that there is a crack in its side proving that even as a child Gorn was a strong little tyke. I can let thee take it for ten gold coins. Dost thou wish to buy the cradle?\\"");', 'message("「那個舊搖籃是野蠻人 Gorn 還是個嬰兒時，晚上用來搖他入睡的搖籃。你可以看到它側邊有條裂縫，這證明 Gorn 從小就是個強壯的小傢伙。我可以讓你用十枚金幣買走。你想買這個搖籃嗎？」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou mayest take it then. I hope that thou dost enjoy it.\\"");', 'message("「那你拿走吧。希望你喜歡。」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou dost not have enough gold!\\"");', 'message("「你沒有足夠的金幣！」");'),
    ('message("A sour look flashes across Beverlea\'s face. \\"Very well. Perhaps I may interest thee in something else.\\"");', 'message("「 Beverlea 臉上閃過一絲不悅的表情。『很好。或許我能讓你對其他東西感興趣。』」");'),
    ('UI_remove_answer("cradle");', 'UI_remove_answer("搖籃");'),
    ('case "rocking horse" attend labelFunc04AD_01B5:', 'case "搖馬" attend labelFunc04AD_01B5:'),
    ('message("\\"This is the rocking horse that once belonged to a little girl from Britain named Diane. She grew to be one of the finest equestriennes to ever sit upon a horse. I could let thee have this rare and unusual piece for twelve gold. Dost thou wish to buy it?\\"");', 'message("「這匹搖馬曾經屬於一位名叫 Diane 的 Britain 小女孩。她長大後成為了騎術最精湛的馬術家之一。我可以讓你用十二枚金幣買下這件稀有而不尋常的物品。你想買嗎？」");'),
    ('message("\\"Then thou art free to take the rocking horse. It is thine!\\"");', 'message("「那你可以隨意帶走這匹搖馬了。它是你的了！」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou dost not have enough money to pay for it!\\"");', 'message("「你沒有足夠的錢買它！」");'),
    ('message("Beverlea rolls her eyes. \\"In a browsing mood, are we? Take thy time.\\"");', 'message("「 Beverlea 翻了翻白眼。『我們只是想隨便看看，是嗎？慢慢看吧。』」");'),
    ('UI_remove_answer("rocking horse");', 'UI_remove_answer("搖馬");'),
    ('case "bell" attend labelFunc04AD_0200:', 'case "鈴鐺" attend labelFunc04AD_0200:'),
    ('message("\\"That bell came from the High Court of Justice in Yew. It was rung to announce that court was in session. I can sell thee that interesting conversation piece for six gold coins.\\tDost thou wish to buy it?\\"");', 'message("「那個鈴鐺來自 Yew 的高等法院。它是用來宣布開庭的。我可以用六枚金幣把這個有趣的話題性物品賣給你。你想買嗎？」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou mayest take thy bell. Use it in good health!\\"");', 'message("「你可以拿走你的鈴鐺。祝你健康地使用它！」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou dost not have enough money to buy it!\\"");', 'message("「你沒有足夠的錢買它！」");'),
    ('message("\\"Not in the mood for a bell today?\\" She wrinkles her lips in the best attempt at a smile. \\"Perhaps something else will strike thy fancy.\\"");', 'message("「今天不想買鈴鐺？』她皺起嘴唇，努力擠出一個微笑。『或許別的東西會合你的心意。』」");'),
    ('UI_remove_answer("bell");', 'UI_remove_answer("鈴鐺");'),
    ('case "hourglass" attend labelFunc04AD_025C:', 'case "沙漏" attend labelFunc04AD_025C:'),
    ('message("\\"I also have an antique hourglass. It was sold to me by this old man who was so daft that he could not recall how to use it! I will sell it to thee for five gold pieces. Dost thou wish to buy it?\\"");', 'message("「我還有一個古董沙漏。這是一個老頭賣給我的，他老糊塗了，連怎麼用都想不起來！我用五枚金幣賣給你。你想買嗎？」");'),
    ('message("\\"I thank thee. Thou mayest take thy glass.\\"");', 'message("「謝謝你。你可以拿走你的沙漏了。」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou dost not have enough money.\\"");', 'message("「你沒有足夠的錢。」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou art not interested in the hourglass?\\" She sighs, \\"Very well. Look around. I have all the time in the world.\\" You catch just a hint of sarcasm in her voice.");', 'message("「你對沙漏沒興趣？』她嘆了口氣，『很好。隨便看看。我有的是時間。』你聽出她語氣中帶著一絲諷刺。」");'),
    ('message("\\"Curse mine old head and failing memory! Has the hourglass already been sold?! No! It must have been stolen! One of the few dishonest people in this town must have taken it!\\"");', 'message("「詛咒我這顆老腦袋和衰退的記憶力！沙漏已經賣掉了嗎？！不！一定是被偷了！這鎮上少數不誠實的人一定把它拿走了！」");'),
    ('UI_remove_answer("hourglass");', 'UI_remove_answer("沙漏");'),
    ('case "spittoon" attend labelFunc04AD_02A8:', 'case "痰盂" attend labelFunc04AD_02A8:'),
    ('message("\\"I also have an old spittoon. It was once used by... a great many people. Thou mayest have it for a gold piece. Take it! Please!\\"");', 'message("「我還有一個舊痰盂。它曾經被……很多人使用過。只要一枚金幣你就可以帶走它。拿走吧！拜託！」");'),
    ('message("\\"I thank thee! Now thou canst go and please do not forget to take it with thee when thou dost leave!\\"");', 'message("「謝謝你！現在你可以走了，請別忘了離開時把它帶走！」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou dost not even have a single gold piece! Nor the decency to inform me that I was wasting my time in talking with thee.\\"");', 'message("「你甚至連一枚金幣都沒有！也沒有體面地告訴我，我和你說話是在浪費時間。」");'),
    ('message("\\"I have many more things in my shop. Many things of high quality and great value as well. Please keep looking.\\"");', 'message("「我店裡還有很多東西。很多高品質且有價值的東西。請繼續看。」");'),
    ('UI_remove_answer("spittoon");', 'UI_remove_answer("痰盂");'),
    ('case "lute" attend labelFunc04AD_02F3:', 'case "魯特琴" attend labelFunc04AD_02F3:'),
    ('message("\\"I have a lute for sale that once belonged to a travelling bard who lost it in a game of dice. I am asking twenty gold coins for it. A song! Wouldst thou like to buy it?\\"");', 'message("「我有一把魯特琴要賣，它曾經屬於一位吟遊詩人，他在擲骰子遊戲中輸掉了它。我開價二十枚金幣。一首歌的價值！你想買嗎？」");'),
    ('message("\\"I thank thee, kind customer. Thou mayest take thy lute. I can see that thou art a true artisan with an appreciation for quality.\\"");', 'message("「謝謝你，親愛的顧客。你可以拿走你的魯特琴了。我看得出你是個懂得欣賞品質的真正藝術家。」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou canst not afford the lute!\\"");', 'message("「你買不起這把魯特琴！」");'),
    ('message("\\"Very well, then. Do keep looking. After all, that is why my shop is here.\\" You thought you could also hear Beverlea mutter to herself for a few moments after saying this, but you are not entirely certain.");', 'message("「『那好吧。請繼續看。畢竟，這就是我開店的目的。』你覺得你還聽到 Beverlea 說完這句話後自言自語了一會兒，但你並不完全確定。」");'),
    ('UI_remove_answer("lute");', 'UI_remove_answer("魯特琴");'),
    ('case "sextant" attend labelFunc04AD_033E:', 'case "六分儀" attend labelFunc04AD_033E:'),
    ('message("\\"I have a sextant that was sold by the world-famous shipwright Owen of Minoc. They are going to be building a monument to him, I understand. Anyway, the sailor who sold it to me had just suffered some harrowing experience out on the waters. He said when he sold it to me that he was going to retire. He obviously did not realize the value of this item. But I can let thee have it for twenty gold pieces. Dost thou wish to buy it?\\"");', 'message("「我有一個 Minoc 世界知名造船匠 Owen 賣的六分儀。我聽說他們打算為他建一座紀念碑。總之，賣給我的水手剛在海上經歷了一些可怕的經驗。他賣給我的時候說他打算退休了。他顯然沒有意識到這件物品的價值。但我可以讓你用二十枚金幣買下它。你想買嗎？」");'),
    ('message("\\"Thou mayest take thy sextant! And may thou always have smooth sailing!\\"");', 'message("「你可以拿走你的六分儀了！願你永遠一帆風順！」");'),
    ('message("\\"I am certain I have something that will interest thee. Browse to thine heart\'s content.\\"");', 'message("「我肯定我有一些你會感興趣的東西。盡情地看吧。」");'),
    ('UI_remove_answer("sextant");', 'UI_remove_answer("六分儀");'),
